<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٣٤٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَقَطَعَ وَهِيَ الْبُوَيْرَةُ،<span class="c5"> فَأَنْزَلَ اللهُ عَزَّ وَجَلَّ:</span> <span class="c3">{مَا قَطَعْتُمْ مِنْ لِينَةٍ}</span>.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>